{"Author": "", "Date": "August 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I have used this app for about a year. You can certainly tell by the reviews the fan base out there, mine is better than yours. In our house we use Siri Google and Alexa so I think I can give an unbiased review. None are perfect but neither are any useless. we tend to use Alexa more because we have prime. The app takes my shopping list, organises my calendar plus allows me to control lights, heating, security and more. It is installed on several android devices and performs differently on each one . It is not perfect but is always evolving. It is definitely fit for purpose."}
