{"Author": "", "Date": "January 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "There's no way provided to replace a failed hub. No way to transfer my many devices, timers etc. There's got to be a better way. Awfully disappointed in the entire Insteon system."}
