{"Author": "Jason Schultz", "Date": "November 22, 2016", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "but app could be better</span> Would be nice to be able to organize devices and scene in room or favorites. App needs to be stream lined and widgets would be nice."}
