{"Author": "", "Date": "October 9, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I find it QUIRKY...   i have three locations.. with cameras at each...have been viewing all three on my Mac book pro safari for several months ... then the system decides I can't view some of my properties.. just get blue screen when I go to them.. call nest and guy.. he says empty cookies... I did that and still have the problem...  i CAN see stuff on chrome but NOT safari... very frustrating"}
{"Author": "Melanie Booth", "Date": "October 16, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Tried to create a new login. Hit submit and got the error message \"Network error. Nest App had trouble communication. \" I have a good Internet connection. Tried a dozen times. Restated my phone. Uninstaller and reinstalled. Anything I could think of, but I get the same message every time."}
{"Author": "Brian Dunn", "Date": "October 2, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I've had the heat be stuck on making my home 82 when it was supposed to heat to 70. I've had the base fail to turn off the AC and cool my home to 65 before I realize it was 75 in the house. And I've had it keep trying to heat the house but fail to turn on the furnace. Never once did it ever warn me or did this \"smart\" thermostat think there was something wrong. Reply to nest message: I've contacted your support in the past &amp; have either told me, \"yeah that would be nice huh?\" Or would send me to the forums    Update: turns my Bluetooth on everytime I open the app and I have to turn it off after closing."}
{"Author": "Mark K", "Date": "October 5, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "How away doesn't work well on the camera...I am getting notifications constantly while I'm at home. It would also be nice if the thermostat portion of the app could give you some details detailed monthly statistics.... That really bugs me"}
{"Author": "Fliss Hope", "Date": "October 10, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Since the last update, every time i open the app it throws up the message about my mobile location. This did not happen before, and i'm not going anywhere different,  and havent changed the settings either!"}
{"Author": "J G", "Date": "October 15, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Touch interface is unresponsive on Galaxy S8 phones. I have 2 nest thermostats in my home and I have to tap multiple times to select the appropriate nest and then adjust the temp. It eventually works but the responsiveness should be much better."}
