{"Author": "Chuck A", "Date": "October 14, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Their app is Such a Joke, Very Deceiving  Waste !! When you supposedly make remote adjustments,  As simple as making   Schedule adjustments, even though they  show on the app screen that the  adjustments you made were changed. The actual Nest Thermostat doesn't  change it's internal adjustments you made using their deceiving app!! I will never buy a Nest Product again!!!! Plus, I am going to let all my new customers,  friends, family and fellow contractors know why not to buy Nest Products Too!!!!"}
{"Author": "Nathan Maust", "Date": "October 12, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Love the overall functionality of the thermostat but HATE the interface and method for adjusting the temperature schedule, especially for Heat/Cool. Why can't that also be arrows like the main screen or even by typing in temps? The slider is maddening, particularly because in Heat/Cool it tends to jump and is difficult to set both temps less than 5 or so degrees apart.  At a minimum why can't ready temp be adjusted independently without the other moving at random?"}
