{"Author": "Rick Nagy", "Date": "September 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "App is great!! Only thing I'd change is with the outdoor cam, a timer on notifications, I don't want notifications all day as my wife and children come and go I want them at night when nobody's supposed to be around our house but the only option is on or off"}
{"Author": "", "Date": "October 4, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The permission list is rediculous. Record audio and video from my phone without permission! Take pictures! The lastest update wants acess to web browser and bookmarks???!!! Sounds suspiciously like data mining and invasion of privacy. How does all this make anyone more secure exactly?"}
{"Author": "Chris C", "Date": "September 19, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "This double notification thing is gone but I am not getting any alerts for my interior camera. I can see it on the timeline though. My wife has ios and it's working fine, only android at this time. Please fix! Defeats the purpose of an interior cam."}
{"Author": "Yan-Fa Li", "Date": "September 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Great app. Gets better over time. One suggestion, for filter reminders, let user configure the size of filter to purchase. Since I do it so infrequently I forget between changings. A place in app to remember that info would be fantastic."}
{"Author": "Angela Foster", "Date": "September 17, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Loved the app until most recent update. Every time I try to open it, i get unexpected error, saying it has stopped working and it closes. So I have yet to be able to open it since last time I updated. So useless app on my phone right now."}
{"Author": "Leon Janzen", "Date": "September 27, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The app and the camera both work well. The reason for the low rating is that I'm quite surprised by the things that the app can't do: it doesn't continue playing in split screen view; it doesn't support casting to a Chromecast; and it seems like it would be an ideal candidate for the new picture-in-picture feature of Android Oreo, but it doesn't do that either. For a Google owned company, these omissions are disappointing."}
{"Author": "David DeLuca", "Date": "September 19, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Home/away assist still doesn't work after lastest update. When trying to use phone location to determine if home or away, the app logs out and doesn't enable (error mentions services are down). Clearing data and reinstalling the app doesn't fix the issue."}
{"Author": "Ben Grantham", "Date": "September 19, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Their thermostats still list \"efficiency\" through a green leaf based on previous temp settings.  According to their spokespeople, these have nothing to do with exterior temperatures, which are a REQUIREMENT for any real efficiencies (estimated or not). Simply figure out the heat transfer rates based on how often the system has to cycle on and off with a specific exterior temperature.       Also, why the heck isn't there any graph of temperature history, let alone one that compares interior to exterior temperature over the course of a month??  Don't you think I'd like to see the effects of added insulation in the attic?   As for their cameras, it's a huge engineering oversight to have the internal IR illumination source always on with the night vision, make it a user switchable function."}
{"Author": "Charlie Waterworth", "Date": "September 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "THANK YOU! For finally fixing the app to allow nest to work outside official territories. Had nest thermostat working perfectly in NZ for years but the app started forcing users to add address and only allowed addresses in officially released countries. Latest app allows addresses from NZ now. Finally the thermostat is smart once again!"}
{"Author": "Pranay Kapadia", "Date": "October 7, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The app forces the phone to turn off repeatedly while viewing the footage. The bluetooth does not turn off even after the successful setup and hence is prone to easy hack by anyone. And There is no option to change the time zone to india. This is a very imp function missing in the app."}
{"Author": "Tra Braxton", "Date": "September 16, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I'm giving 3 instead of the 2. I'm having a very hard time connecting to my Galaxy note 3. It doesn't connect as easy as described"}
{"Author": "Paul M", "Date": "September 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Latest update seems to have fixed double notifications and location for home away is working again but I still have to manually set to away. Arriving home it automatically switches to home."}
{"Author": "", "Date": "September 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Getting double notifications for every alert. One seems to be first motion then the second alerts with the preview of what's going on. Quite annoying."}
{"Author": "Dwayne Nelson", "Date": "September 22, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Doesn't work well anymore - had the highest electric bill in a while because thermostat keeps saying I'm home when I'm not"}
{"Author": "Matt Vertex", "Date": "September 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "This app is slow slow..My Wi-Fi router is 5ft from it and there Is a 22sec delay..And now it's 12pm and I can't even watch the camera because there's a network error when I click on the app to watch the camera"}
{"Author": "Daniel Vittorelli", "Date": "September 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Not talking about the app itself but the thermostat sucks, even if you turn off learning and schedule it still does it's thing and temperatures are never where you want them :("}
{"Author": "", "Date": "September 19, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The app is ok but now the thermostat has disconnected from Wi-Fi and won't reconnect.. I guess an update broke it and you're not going to patch it anytime soon.. Poor show for a company that makes so much profit."}
{"Author": "Chorba Leng", "Date": "September 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Update: womp womp.. Camera randomly turns on even though it it set to \"Home\" and I'm home! Back to ****  Update: geofencing finally worked! Thank you! 5 stars!   Previous version: 4 stars because I can't rate 3.5 stars. Reasons being:  1. I had to use my laptop to set up the camera coz the app wouldn't/can't recognize the camera. It also took a while on my laptop (Mac) because it didn't automatically start like what were usually used to. I think what caused the installation issue on the app is that my router has two frequencies and the nest cam takes a different one over my phone..? I dunno.. But anyway, I got it to install and it's all good now. \u263a 2. Geofencing does not work. It's a small issue. I only have to manually tell the app that I'm either home or away. But it would be nice if it worked and does the switching over for me.  Other than those two issues, I love the camera! Does exactly what I want and need it to do. I got the camera because my fire alarms at home set off for no reason while I'm at work. Police and fire department went to my house to make sure everything was OK only to find out it was a false alarm."}
{"Author": "Aaron Lew.", "Date": "September 27, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Why are you wanting permission to spy on my device/app history?! This is unacceptable!"}
{"Author": "Tim Anslow", "Date": "September 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Oreo: issue with location based functionality is back again. Yay."}
{"Author": "Massimo Gatti", "Date": "September 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Provide a geofence customization feature please. To control 186$ thermostat I expect a better app, more configurable and smart."}
{"Author": "Chad Andrist", "Date": "September 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Now getting double notifications on my Nest cameras and the push to talk doesn't work. It used to work fine, not anymore."}
{"Author": "Travis Poole", "Date": "September 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I am using a Panasonic toughpad and I cannot view live video. I can view recorded video just fine. It is using android 5.1.1"}
{"Author": "", "Date": "September 19, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Not working for the last few days"}
{"Author": "Shaun Smith", "Date": "September 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Great app but cloud services overpriced"}
{"Author": "Anna Chesnokova", "Date": "September 15, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Great job!"}
{"Author": "James McAlister", "Date": "September 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "App is a great companion for the hardware.  Better options for outdoor notifications a must."}
{"Author": "John Ellis", "Date": "September 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Much better after recent update"}
{"Author": "Carol Ramirez", "Date": "September 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Ve it"}
{"Author": "junior arevalo", "Date": "September 27, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "the best. ."}
