{"Author": "Brian Larsen", "Date": "September 7, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The app works fine, but it's difficult to fast forward or rewind just a few seconds. More precise scrolling would be helpful."}
{"Author": "Jim Toussaint", "Date": "September 7, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Awful. The home and away function just does not work. Requires endless manual overrides. I've tried all the tips. Awful. Awful. Awful"}
