{"Author": "Jason Marshall", "Date": "September 2, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Since last update, I keep getting vibrating notifications every hour or so even though I'm not opening the app. Also, I keep getting \"This application is running in the background\" notifications every little while as well on my Google Pixel running Android 8.0 (Oreo). Very annoying. Will uninstall if not fixed soon."}
{"Author": "Jared Schwanz", "Date": "September 28, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Looks like my last review was deleted, so I'll post it again. My thermostat stopped working properly after about a year, but didn't know until a little later. I called customer \"service,\" and they verified that it doesn't work properly. They offer a voucher for a new one, which is garbage so I refused, they should replace the unit because it should last much longer. The senior rep argues with me for a while, then hangs up on me mid sentence. Do not buy this!"}
{"Author": "Matt Allen", "Date": "September 4, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Issue with a brief notification appearing and dissappearing after a split second causing me to uninstall the app. This happens 24/7 when the app is in the background and every time I open the app causing the notification tone to go off and wake the device."}
