{"Author": "", "Date": "September 3, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I'm enjoying my new security outside camera that I bought 24 hours ago the only problem is they need to improve on the alerts with the people walking by it does not notify me all the time it works only half the time this is the only complaint I have besides that the HD is unbelievable along with the night vision which is like daytime very good product but I would recommend it I would have gave it a five-star but it wasn't for the problem with the alert with people please fix this problem thank you very much I will be adding more cameras in the future"}
{"Author": "le corbusier", "Date": "September 1, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Very good app. Allows control of heating remotely and is saving me a small fortune in my holiday rental. Very easy to use for me and 'old school' users. Minimal, unobtrusive, yet stylish design reflected all the way down to the packaging."}
{"Author": "Cason Pham", "Date": "September 5, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Glad you got it together! Cam, Protect, and Thermostat--all in one. Thanks for implementing GIF snapshot notification. Four stars due to no Chromecast support."}
