{"Author": "Luke Barney", "Date": "September 1, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Latest update causes notification 'updating your phones location for home/away assist' every 30s.  Have turned off home assist and still doing it!  Please fix"}
