{"Author": "Sethanos", "Date": "August 13, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Beyond horrible. Where to start, app functionality leaves a lot to be desired. Sometimes the options work and sometimes they don't. Add in the fact the company wants to bend you over and go to town on you for a subscription is nothing short of horrific. A cloud save is an amazing service that provides a backup. It should NOT be forced down our throats. No offence Nest, but I simply don't trust you with what happens in my house. Wish I never bought your camera."}
{"Author": "Rogier Hoogmolen", "Date": "August 22, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Love the app. But there is something I would like to see changed, as I encountered a issue during the holiday. Is there a possibility during the next upgrade to have the option to turn a nest protect module off. Because we had one nest protect module hone haywire when we were on holiday and not the option to shut it off. I can understand that this can be an obnoxious sound for our neighbors when this occurs at night or during the weekend."}
{"Author": "Phillip Stephens", "Date": "August 30, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The home/away assist just simply does not work. Tryed nocking all sensors off and just using my phone's location, still doesn't switch to away. Been on the phone to customer support. Gone through all the settings and all are correct.  So home away assist simply does not work and I'm not the only person to say this in reviews!!"}
{"Author": "Stacey N", "Date": "August 13, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "This app used to work great with my indoor cam. Since the recent update, it is terrible! It does not recognize my phone and the home away/assist feature does not work anymore! Disappointing! Complete annoying to have an update that makes the product nonfunctional!"}
{"Author": "Devashish Haldar", "Date": "August 23, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Probably the worst app today on Android. For many many months the app is broken and doesn't register the touch commands. I've to press literally 10 times before something happens. As far as the product goes, haven't tried the competition yet but the self learning is a big joke. I reach home almost at the same time everyday but the device happily keeps the AC off until I wave in front of it to wake it up."}
{"Author": "John Doe", "Date": "August 10, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "1. Please add notifications, like if the pin is entered incorrectly 2. Let us to set the amount of time before it dims/turns the display off 3. Add a timer option so I can set it to turn on/off in X amount of time 4. Allow us to set the schedule to turn it on/off 5. Allow us to set auto-away to \"on\" for the less tech savvy people so all they have to do is walk by the Nest to end away so they get A/C or heat 6. Add a lock icon on the home screen and main screen of the Thermostat so we know it's locked 7. Please add a timer for whichever setting we put it on for x amount of time 8. For the family member, please make it so we can choose who can access what on the Nest Thermostat and allow us to only let them change the temperature if they choose to 9. Let us temporarily suspend any other member for any amount of time"}
{"Author": "Josh Fanslow", "Date": "August 18, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Do not purchase nest cameras cameras keep going off line and someone broke into my house and because camera was offline did not catch anyone on camera I called to see if they can be tracked and they can not. Also they would not replace camera even though they were stolen and can not be traced because camera was not working properly camera was only 5ft away from wifi no excuse. Purchase arlo they seem to be much better without issue of going offline and it's free to monitor unlike nest."}
{"Author": "Droning with Kyle", "Date": "August 17, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The home away assist doesn't work, even had phone only location for home/away still thinks I'm home even the app says not here. It continues to be set as home, using more energy. Thought the point was for this to use less energy. Nest support has not helped either."}
{"Author": "Phil Rizzudo", "Date": "August 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Cancelled my monthly service because of this app. Dropcam app worked well. This app does not. The scanner doesn't work to scan your equipment at all in any way. Not worth the trouble and inconvenience to hook it up to my computer for setup. Getting rid of Nest all together because of this. My alarm company will add better ,monitored, camera for same cost as nest. $10/month."}
{"Author": "Jon Bradley", "Date": "August 20, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The app for the nest cams and review is basically unusable. Scrollability is terrible. 15s back/fwd doesn't work. Very poor playback quality"}
{"Author": "Dominic Hoffmann", "Date": "August 25, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "App became faster and more responsive. Thanks for adding the activity snapshot's. Keep up the good work. If there would be a tweak to minimize the bandwidth more. Even on low setting, it still consuming a lot of data."}
{"Author": "Caleb Beddes", "Date": "August 12, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Works well. Sometimes, I have to tap twice to open what I want to open, or do what I want to do.  That's a minor inconvenience. I'd love to have the temperature history available. Perhaps on a graph with the outside temperature.  Additionally I think it'd be good to see when the fan ran in the energy usage graph. Not just the heating and cooling. All in all, a functional app."}
{"Author": "Scott Baker", "Date": "August 27, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Great concept, poor execution.  Alerts are great.  Live watch is very good. Timeline review is horrible and navigation of video review is 90s level, just lazy/cheap.  The app doesn't do the hardware justice."}
{"Author": "Kevin Moffat", "Date": "August 23, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Generally works really well, but two things I'd love to see implemented would be customisable notification sounds and the ability to view saved clips through the app. Otherwise this works flawlessly. Pixel on Nougat 7.1.2"}
