{"Author": "Ennis Glendon", "Date": "August 25, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Home/Away assist using phone location is a COMPLETE JOKE. Give us a way to adjust threshold for GPS drift and/or time away. Constantly getting alerts for my Nest cam when I am at home. Really obnoxious implementation."}
{"Author": "Brooks Howell", "Date": "August 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "The back button at the top left is impossibly hard to press and takes about 15 presses to properly register. Also, the video timeline is very hard to control properly. Randomly jumps at the slightest movement of my thumb."}
{"Author": "Steve Thomas", "Date": "August 14, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I haven't been able to sign in and register my products since Friday, app accepts my username and password but than I get \"There was a problem connecting to the Nest services. Please try again in a few minutes\" 4 days and I haven't been able to use the service. Connected Twitter, they're no help. I'm told several other Canadians are having this issue. No tweet to say there is an issue and nothing updated on your website to identify an issue. If multiple users are effected why not post something. I feel like I'm just getting brushed off. All my wasted time I feel you should pay me"}
{"Author": "Timothy O", "Date": "September 1, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "I don't know what happened in the update on 8/31/17 but now I'm getting seemingly duplicate notifications for people/motion alerts. It's like it throws both now instead of one or the other (people vs motion)."}
{"Author": "Julia Mason", "Date": "August 13, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "My parents just purchased the indoor cam for their home and it fails to alert whether or not any one is there, some features aren't working and the camera overheats. So instead of someone being in the house as the many worry we have to worry about fire."}
