{"Author": "Andrew Taylor", "Date": "July 2, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Ridiculous software engineering... as a computer scientist this is plain poor design. It forces users to update or else punishes them with reduced functionality... AKA blackmail. Typical from Philips! Sad."}
