{"Author": "Tso Chen", "Date": "October 2, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Edit: Getting better but still not great. Firmware update fails and there's no way for me to force update. It's all luck on when the app decides to tell me if there is update available.  Piece of garbage. No linking of device to any unique account means if your app data gets corrupted, you've lost control of your device until the next time you go home. Thats a huge oversight for something meant to be managed remotely. To the person that calls the rest of us dumb as rocks. What a fantastic review. So very helpful."}
