{"Author": "Derek Norfield", "Date": "October 3, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "A bit temperamental but so much easier than groping for key while carrying \"stuff\""}
{"Author": "Diego Terzano", "Date": "October 13, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Terrible piece of software. Works intermittently, crashes constantly (on 7.1.2) and it is frustrating to use."}
{"Author": "James Carter", "Date": "October 10, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 1 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Does not work with Android Oreo. I feel like I wasted my money on this lock."}
{"Author": "Tori Cantales", "Date": "October 13, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 3 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Half the time it doesn't want to connect to our lock and we have to spend forever trying to unlock it... Idk if it is our app that is not working or something wrong with the lock itself"}
{"Author": "Richard Ferguson", "Date": "September 16, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 4 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Was able to email a key to a guest so they could enter the house before we got there. Worked great, no problem at all."}
{"Author": "lisa morgan", "Date": "September 16, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Try to modify an ekey &amp; the app crashes. Galaxy s8+"}
