{"Author": "Roslyn Hearne", "Date": "September 19, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Says that update is required on my Galaxy S6, but will not update.  Will not allow me to assign any other keys.  Sucks!"}
{"Author": "Derek Gleaves", "Date": "September 21, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Doesn't work really with my Samsung Galaxy S8+  seems to work well with the fob or other phones"}
{"Author": "Chris Gates", "Date": "September 12, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 2 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "No Note 8 support. Dumb."}
