{"Author": "Miguel Gil", "Date": "September 25, 2017", "Stars": " Rated 5 stars out of five stars ", "Text": "Yes kevo now working on my Note 8 confirmed on my mom's my dads and my sister's note 8 also \ud83d\ude00\ud83d\ude06\ud83d\ude06\ud83d\udc4d\ud83d\udc4d\ud83d\udc4d"}
